race.comment: HARD STYLE GIRL (3) won by a neck last start when getting around this track 400m in an enormous 22.27. Should be in this for a long way. FOLDING STUFF (1) was well fancied in betting last start but could only manage 6 lengths away in third (19.56). Can feature again. OVERFLOW JENNY (5) won as punters' elect last time and is sure to feature again.
